{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "29ad5d6d-1828-410f-bab8-125dfe50c708", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/29ad5d6d-1828-410f-bab8-125dfe50c708@1.pkg/1772597665888/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597666896", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/29ad5d6d-1828-410f-bab8-125dfe50c708@1.pkg/1772597665888/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597666896"}, "identifier": "29ad5d6d-1828-410f-bab8-125dfe50c708", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">本题考查敬畏生命。</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">B：分析题文，题目中7名市民面对他人生命危险时，主动参与救援积极施救，体现了对他人生命的尊重和关爱；故B符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">A：题干未涉及个人利益；故A不符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">C：侧重&ldquo;自救能力&rdquo;，而题干是救助他人，故C与题意不符；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">D：强调个人生活态度，未体现救助他人的社会责任感；故D不符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">故本题选B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）持续的暴雨让路面积水，一辆小汽车陷入深水中。危急时刻，7名市民挺身而出跳入积水中，与民警协力紧急救援，被困的司机最终获救。7名市民传递的正能量是(&nbsp;&n